title: KU football begins tough stretch at West Chester Sunday
text:
KU football begins tough stretch at West Chester Sunday Golden Bears eyeing third-straight win Published: 7 MIN. AGO Kutztown gearing up for tough test at West Chester KUTZTOWN, Pa. - 
Kutztown picked up its second straight PSAC East win against Millersville over the weekend. 
But the schedule gets considerably tough for the Golden Bears down the back half of the season. 
That begins Saturday with a road trip to West Chester. Quick Clicks 
KU was able to pound the rock against the Marauders. They're hoping to carry that over into this weekend.
